{"tid":1895983,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[集思廣益] 如何避過班狗打擊鄉黑","createTime":"2020-02-25T00:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T11:41:17.000Z","uid":94771,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3f398a038ee048b5293258869b11281a79849c","tid":1895983,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"銀髮手足檔口比鄉黑搞！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fcLojS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fcLojS</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論唔同方向<br />\n６月個時，大家有唔同意見都好值得參考<br />\n希望大家一齊討論，一千人一千種意見<br />\n咩天馬行空都拎出來<br />\n<br />\n班鄉黑依家有班狗保護住，所以正面就應該好難了，對狗＋鄉黑難度大個天<br />\n<br />\n1. 係水，電落手？不過要潛入去難度好大<br />\n2. 網線落手，３ｍｂ都無得佢用？<br />\n3. 定向喇叭，晚晚嘈"},{"pid":"e31a08c05bcdc78fe6342a1c3f22efbeaa18e0b9","tid":1895983,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認真Post無人理"},{"pid":"2d177c4914bfa876fccd2add312f06dbca60ab98","tid":1895983,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T01:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ad266eef9ff1daa4e652dc018e15b041df42d4","tid":1895983,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"一齊諗諗"},{"pid":"fec6017cda5a00c0e7d7987ca5b1b5d09adc8475","tid":1895983,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff855dda5cd8d1ff14d1fd260e7b704213c239b","tid":1895983,"uid":120916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:46:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e98496a312c1d0272aaa7d3aca2c757ccca479ce","tid":1895983,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:51:39.000Z","msg":"留意佢地晚聚腳點 睇鋪邊間<br />\n認人認樣"},{"pid":"12f9851cae3a47d61188fad6